    ,
    
    
    "Airbag units must not come into contact with grease, oil, cleaning agents, liquids or similar substances."
    ,
    
    
    "Do not expose airbag units to temperatures of more than 90 °C."
    ,
    
    
    "Do not remove the short-circuit spring on the plug contacts."
    ,
    
    
    "Triggering and preparations may only be carried out by skilled staff, supervised by a second responsible person."
    ,
    
    
